OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,FCompensation payments to Birmingham
OL,7,Fbin workers worth up to #20,000 would
OL,8,Fnot expose the council to new equal
OL,9,Fpay claims, new legal advice shows.
OL,11,FIn a new briefing shared with Unite
OL,12,Fthe Union, top employment lawyers have
OL,13,Fadvised that Birmingham City Council's
OL,14,Fwarnings about potential equal pay
OL,15,Fliabilities are "significantly
OL,16,Foverstated" and have little basis in
OL,17,Flaw.
