OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,FThe union says the advice from Oliver
OL,7,FSegal KC and Stuart Brittenden KC,
OL,8,Fboth leading employment barristers,
OL,9,Fmakes clear that paying the
OL,10,Fcompensation would not lead to fresh
OL,11,Fclaims because the refuse workers are
OL,12,Fin "very different material
OL,13,Fcircumstances" from other potential
OL,14,Fequal pay claimants.
OL,16,FUnite says this is because the bin
OL,17,Fworkers have taken industrial action
OL,18,Fand have been affected by council
OL,19,Factions, including "fire and rehire".
