OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,FHundreds of refuse workers have been
OL,7,Fon strike for more than six months
OL,8,Fover the removal of the Waste
OL,9,FRecycling Collection Officer role that
OL,10,Fthe union says could result in pay
OL,11,Fcuts of up to #8,000.
OL,13,FUnite says a "ballpark" deal was
OL,14,Freached in talks with council
OL,15,Fofficials at ACAS in July but was
OL,16,Flater withdrawn.
