OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,FThe offer, which included one-off
OL,7,Fcompensation payments of between
OL,8,F#14,000 and #20,000 per worker, was
OL,9,Fagreed in principle between Unite's
OL,10,FGeneral Secretary and the council's
OL,11,FManaging Director, Joanne Roney.
OL,13,FBut the Union claims that the
OL,14,Fagreement was later blocked by
OL,15,Fgovernment-appointed commissioners
OL,16,Fworking at the authority.
OL,18,FThe council said it had been forced to
OL,19,Fwalk away from talks as it had reached
OL,20,Fthe "limit" of what it could offer.
