OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,FThe union says the council has since
OL,7,Frefused to restart formal negotiations
OL,8,Fand is pressing ahead with plans to
OL,9,Fdowngrade jobs.
OL,11,FOliver Segal KC said: "They can't
OL,12,Fbring additional equal pay claims so
OL,13,Fthey would have to bring indirect
OL,14,Fdiscrimination claims.
OL,16,F"In order to succeed in those claims,
OL,17,Fthey would have to show that the
OL,18,Fcouncil was treating everybody the
OL,19,Fsame, which it isn't.
