OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,F"More importantly, they'd have to show
OL,7,Fthat they, the equal pay claimants,
OL,8,Fwere in the same or similar
OL,9,Fcircumstances to the refuse workers,
OL,10,Fand then not because the refuse
OL,11,Fworkers have good legal claims for
OL,12,Fadditional sums like redundancy and
OL,13,Funfair dismissal claims."
OL,15,FHe adds that the council could settle
OL,16,Fits current disputes with Unite
OL,17,F"comfortably within its present
OL,18,Fbudget" without triggering new equal
OL,19,Fpay liabilities.
