OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,FUnite also claims the council has
OL,7,F"massively overestimated" its equal
OL,8,Fpay costs in the past - that resulted,
OL,9,Fin part, in the council declaring
OL,10,Feffective bankruptcy.
OL,12,FTwo years ago the authority suggested
OL,13,Fit might owe #760 million, but ITV
OL,14,FNews understands that the true figure
OL,15,Fis around #300 million.
OL,17,FThe council has said it has its own
OL,18,Flegal advice on the issue but has not
OL,19,Freleased it publicly.
