OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,FA council spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,FCouncil does not recognise or agree
OL,8,Fwith Unite's position. We must pay
OL,9,Ffairly and equitably across the
OL,10,Fcouncil in all circumstances.
OL,12,F"Having reached a landmark agreement
OL,13,Fto settle equal pay claims in
OL,14,FBirmingham, we will not perpetuate the
OL,15,Fmistakes of the past and re-open the
OL,16,Fpotential for equal pay claims by
OL,17,Fmaking potentially unlawful payments
OL,18,Fto settle the waste dispute.
