OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1761079688
OL,3,CPay offer to end Birmingham bin strike
OL,4,Cwould not result in equal pay claims
OL,6,F"The council has not undertaken a
OL,7,F'fire and rehire' exercise. The
OL,8,Fcouncil has conducted collective and
OL,9,Findividual consultation in excess of
OL,10,Fstatutory requirements when a
OL,11,Fredundancy situation occurs, and this
OL,12,Fhas resulted in the vast majority of
OL,13,Femployees accepting an alternative
OL,14,Frole with the council."
OL,16,FThe union is calling on councillors
OL,17,Fand political parties to push for
OL,18,Frenewed talks and to support a deal
OL,19,Fbased on the original "ballpark"
OL,20,Fproposal discussed at ACAS.
